                <div class="rendering rendering_researchoutput  rendering_researchoutput_apa rendering_contributiontojournal rendering_apa rendering_contributiontojournal_apa">Prieto-Alhambra, D., Lalmohamed, A., Abrahamsen, B., Arden, N. K., de Boer, A., Vestergaard, P., &amp; de Vries, F. (2014). <a rel="ContributionToJournal" href="https://cris.maastrichtuniversity.nl/en/publications/oral-bisphosphonate-use-and-total-kneehip-implant-survival-valida/" class="link"><span>Oral Bisphosphonate Use and Total Knee/Hip Implant Survival: Validation of Results in an External Population-Based Cohort</span></a>. <a rel="Journal" href="#" class="link"><span><em>Arthritis &amp; Rheumatology</em></span></a>, <em>66</em>(11), 3233-3240. <a onclick="window.open(this.href, '_blank','noopener,noreferrer'); return false;" href="https://doi.org/10.1002/art.38789" class="link"><span>https://doi.org/10.1002/art.38789</span></a></div>
